patthana16.7:4.1: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naabyākatassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:4.2: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo nakusalassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:4.3: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naakusalassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:4.4: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naakusalassa naappaccayassa ca naabyākatassa naappaccayassa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:4.5: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo nakusalassa naappaccayassa ca naakusalassa naappaccayassa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. #5
